items.title: 9-year-old dies after incident at Hersheypark's water park, CEO says
items.description: A 9-year-old child has died after an incident at The Boardwalk water park at Hersheypark in Hershey, Pennsylvania, on Thursday.

items.title: Man falls to his death during Oasis concert in London
items.description: Oasis said that its members are "shocked and saddened" after a man fell to his death during a concert by the band at London's Wembley Stadium.

items.title: New Medicaid federal work requirements mean less leeway for states
